### HTTP Request

`POST http://localhost:3000/api/webhooks`


### POST Parameters

Parameter | Default / Type | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
data | {} | The root element of your JSON post object.
type | webhooks | Resource the object represents.
attributes | {} | The object that contains all the pertanent information about the order.
attributes[url] | nil | String: the URL to receive callback notifications
attributes[enabled] | true | Boolean
attributes[received] | true | Boolean
attributes[design-downloaded] | false | Boolean
attributes[processed] | true | Boolean
attributes[shipped] | true | Boolean
attributes[cancelled] | true | Boolean
attributes[printed] | false | Boolean
attributes[pressed] | false | Boolean
attributes[cut] | false | Boolean
attributes[sewn] | false | Boolean
attributes[turned] | false | Boolean
attributes[packed] | false | Boolean

